完全沒有踩雷\\n連招待的shot都好好喝我的天\\n完全值得五星,之後一定會再來??\", \"author_name\": \"旻旻\"}, {\"text\": \"調酒很有台灣味，主要是用新鮮水果及茶酒做搭配，連喝四杯皆無踩雷?\\n\\n調酒師介紹詳細且熱情，店內氛圍放鬆舒適，非常值得前來體驗??\", \"author_name\": \"鄭阿哲\"}, {\"text\": \"調酒餐點皆優秀，服務人員講解也都很熱心，會主動關心酒跟餐點口味\", \"author_name\": \"AW\"}, {\"text\": \"服務非常棒！食物好吃飲料好喝！氣氛很讚，輕鬆舒服\", \"author_name\": \"柴史蒂夫\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmu8QfN9m7GDGMJvH2Xj9f3MnGZR6I8Li0wZQelILEnZhbwe1Sx7SYVx-TUx1eZyZvrP_r_VmclKt0RG9j1SohR5iwAbGpKC8j3sgL50CasjmrAyiBL0kU7aVWY_5XfCV-IsmjFB_JP1rDlP8Cg8oUu62aClLg2tTUpwDqnsonG7nZk\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnfFiLRdQpUaTb8Tltik7BMxYtMNrSCclzi1McroloGG4S-DPHg6DuGmxqqaj8Q-ZPbw0RwYkC7lSwy0x12HM9r2lUzeOSl9TtkhJMAAGLOzHomDxBjiZsJ5Q6noU530fIYimAGlAVu7KdO5Mlis4rBbrN9m73DDYYoKrAhmnknbD7B\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZl8WHTx0-PadBbQMyj0RedIBq33jF93mDpdGK_h_r8ftE3grQRy1KRRiKkCcWsYl3e1zulmrbZc07uLqdCNVo8eUMvyF6MxH-fkvGXzXOYbZBf5MQ2uYT8eqAqYI33fV9CQBin28rV74s5AWgwVcf4m4C0u8JsmDbkZjJSLZ1f3QdWv\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkalzUNdAmNMJDFW6ZWywbl_nejG-qkejxLXBvF-_dXOifAYHEowG9AWjDFwTHIuGui68KRVfthbBJMC07uVo_LZ-8XJQ5OXuEerRZ0GX3CdeAu9uZAHAex1y4eqk7ipJ3X_szrIV-TGjGJHyjvolj9O5eaqSdiip3GdmVdVyoR4vDQ\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnibOuwRZgk0W9il-zOeBlxmaUUribjHz6dOYxgpRpNEa5A2vEsb0p0RKKbIeO_v4dFlV9iP88qf8Rjf-S2luVzEYCPG_hul6IA3fDLjcHW-XWpB1djGGjTrlgGq3rkcrqgX41AKKS9XhBWX1xaw_e5tvh_OqZXs7anpbfFq9vmvkPp\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkQZkEU4sbA_JHh4T-c8sEMXYN9i0FWjzNGBDW3-1HSAUut8nLnjdaeBks21-N8hS7z2QAjQT3vWEGba-R3aCkptkKH6akGApo8BdrorN21WujJNq4lo8be_2kzUvlupWuVfzTCxOhkogzW0YRNKsXvdcb8gxZ4kMhrRfD_q6wYtLgy\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZm9bwQw9sp9Ib1Xbi-36eirO4UMRqFHqBg-lBBC5Bc4NSF2aGRUr0R5fzKLHPomNnJb1vJT5AjCfjtaQGEAuun_Ym60hCa9EgkceEUO8ZrVv