 tipsy. However, in the next morning, with a clear head, we realized that we got charged for an extra drink! We did not order Taiwanese beer but it was on the billing list! We were charged an extra 180 NT for that! The one who took our order was the boss of this bar, as mentioned in the receipt. The bar was definitely not crowded  when we were having our drink. So we highly doubt that they did this on purpose, not a mistake. Even though 180NT did not worth our time reasoning with them, we will never go to this bar again or recommended it to anyone.\", \"author_name\": \"J L\"}]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZk7K13K8n8BXLw-NQvp_5a7u8t8nmv6q9vJbYbYLAk2AYB6xAFsPHHNUjQlmsUA0-Dfh7MtctN1aapOq5v6FKn8APjkg_HVyV5go82B40_A3jnbBSnumZskWKiAVNqogEIwCgMvRGWWQ5domlq9cvFgnUwEW31b0OxuGl6Z8SvYnGiA\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlEgEKi4JqZGMQl7JFd1QhKXLcvfAKsx93J6odkYsjSNr0BMXh9-MVMkQpfmgh8J3d9z8jOgLlkCGhpZfG_SeiEBoYJtgwAZ2MpSYoSoxPRP7xlsbhXVzmUhFfObz0KuwMYCcX8LImP-nL6vlQWuFzekRXb7MJ1GkN5H419DJLrnuT-\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlsW3Eu6pPEyVVIIPHfEu1Jhq7DWeUUhr4FgXXg7pRmihZhvrba_e34S52xPuv3GtaVoeDoVtRDly9fvhHDeRQYLwh9I4OeVHyDTc2PYLG1FikSO2Ci-Qz4wmESu6eXR9WSfld0kAdQ-lSP5rlCWu29L72nR2zcRTKCc7ym3svKLRYY\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZn2UOd45-PqoVLWjBXPLs1s7QmZt2T-zQ6B4RGg0Nf3N8-8g0_UJDLMYo1epzhA3rUsxvpzjkAGShRyUg5R4zN-9alaYGPZhrdjRE0QxAL7TyUCmhedyIIExLjXomwb3AYpCjqJh132RTaNX2bSOS3Zs6_SP-Lrs_PD4h-L6T3w0GQG\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkgXGg1rmmG0akc8kbbWZySTaxtXZ3RiN1usqNIbqL4O8T351iNmrDbN3t7hEzoFkn_2uOZnqJ6Gf7hjlQXR-SZdU7O-YVek_ds8ExNkK_k4lymIXTjioKXdYT17_NodT6zWaij7tRGQUcqTtttiYhrFl-uT7V88F5VmyfMVdQp0Cz2\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlKkv8xczrydeZ1tQPoOD8oFtn_9FPXFDLOckWh0KsGXz3zXeVHxYDmPvS7Gjhv5dkg7nx5FuvOlvaOQisL70SzY6QJuOPxYYty4foyh