酒喜歡Plum John Collins & Snow bird Old fashion ?\\n\\n唯一的缺點應該是冷氣超冷，我們換了兩次位子還是很冷，要來的人記得帶外套。\", \"author_name\": \"YL C\"}, {\"text\": \"因為有在追蹤林老師的Youtube頻道，今天終於有機會來店裡體驗，沒想到是家小而美的酒吧，從現場氛圍到服務人員以及酒品等，都非常令人滿意?。是會再去的一家店。\", \"author_name\": \"Speic Lu\"}, {\"text\": \"服務很好 介紹的很詳細\\n\\n威士忌專業 調酒很弱\\n\\n魯肉飯好吃\\n\\n煙燻鮭魚一般\\n\\n低消800/人\", \"author_name\": \"柯\"}, {\"text\": \"巷子裡面的威士忌博物館，店長很會詳細介紹每款酒的香味及製作過程，適合幾人小酌的好去處\", \"author_name\": \"fanny li\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnxsXuPAPJ-Tsv1Vdti-FdSZXLJhjBnmqi26LuKsAFKJPHQTZsf65vvgzpRsbQAoRzLJQW6sxVRxYaTnBlDuUxb-7bqBol6Ar0GSxSSHAcyQ-Ra9FcOdIOgzYronJ_0CeNxYLLG5V262Fyrg7UfBgS2bFSynhl5al4umgSAC4-qGEGl\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnOjVqY-hHYnQZTvTxbLqU_mHzcB1TEb8iZH_k6d9RW6QcCJLbx2pS31RmGrbexOxInqH7JinquA_zdiqaa3EEyl7-G9Mz2yi7Hk8SSHqQgYJq-HKHRK-iN_fRlDUOyTLnhHrU29NTKOSOeOb_nxs7ijQC9ZKBX5vEp6Dkk-GXw9L_I\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZl4_sehdaeKPQ9wlsa0ehVSXmnIbWV5ow7M3-G4Q0ENN2P1pXyoORM0qVYERPCJj8iWTxWKfJh3JT-7HaeF_Wd7H46r57B7dKErrBxNC52D0FZeFw4G09FOWraRgnNac2s8z1qDdDFYtt6Nu46f7fWQFisAdRYv0OT2vX-6snts7_em\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmyBBd4uZzO4yGNXzteuf75N208CZiq63A3WlcCp1OiBRs5qBwHGxOWDHYeb0JKSgLJnAPoKU1SR5rnWXrLpPC9EqPPSTzA0TiIZd0CuJ3a_0PBxqIiTVoAFJ8P4Il3BdunMuCBt2phVD8d4h-p0Hj3qys11OGw2BZEsvxrICjmif3B\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnqt16voU4DgLllaLtsM8A-9ok_qwFVnmW3nL6zjn1k2dLfUm6BdBrA428VN2kATyqj9dqy27pgb3g1lA9z7Mp3jprF5lvnxnSpPDf-WhCKmlwOTyW3q_kZ09BwXJZEdu-SenUodK49vyBnmHKZ2_eSSh563ux94PvfZi2LpuZG_mFd\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnSXx2MCHt0AdD9ssydEjPM5hnDUyYuz9IM-qExdN2-VCC561LJG-C3d6keYbpRn7cSKUI-clWiRQXZ6bPBnuWgN15V30uQWv-lXsUamgsNVpyj0_K_-CYMu4oR9XmvLKR8Y95zLTcBSyPqqzruxQWmm8cACm1GI0VKsNVtkFvL4nGR\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\":