北市萬華區武昌街二段83-2號','02 2331 1145','[\"星期一: 19:00 – 02:00\", \"星期二: 19:00 – 02:00\", \"星期三: 19:00 – 02:00\", \"星期四: 19:00 – 02:00\", \"星期五: 18:00 – 02:30\", \"星期六: 18:00 – 02:30\", \"星期日: 19:00 – 02:00\"]','[{\"text\": \"位於武昌街樂聲影院旁，店內精釀啤酒種類繁多，也有簡易調酒跟炸物等下酒菜，老闆親切，人員服務也很到位。店內空間不大，人多時稍顯擁擠吵雜。營業到晚上2點，是夜貓族的好去處！\", \"author_name\": \"Ren-Shyong Fang\"}, {\"text\": \"♡♡♡♡\\n-\\n吧台都能精準按照每個人的喜好推薦適合的選項\\n-\\n5號飲品/台虎電音趴 473ml?250\\n❤️冰箱內啤酒Apple Lambic beer ?？\\n這瓶好好喝?\\n-\\n低消每人300\", \"author_name\": \"Abigail Chen\"}, {\"text\": \"電影街內\\n位子不多 有兩桌戶外座位\\n有一些精釀瓶裝酒.台灣精釀\\n有低消 有小電視球賽轉播\\n服務態度很好?不收服務費\", \"author_name\": \"xx Chuang\"}, {\"text\": \"店員服務態度好也很漂亮！酒也很好喝?\\n已經二訪了❤️❤️，下次再帶朋友來喝！\", \"author_name\": \"cheukying ho\"}]','[{\"text\": \"粗魯的工作人員，在一次誤會和一個酒友為我忘記付錢的兩瓶啤酒付錢之後。回來過幾次。然後我又回來了，然後碰巧那個在酒友蓋上標籤時正在工作的女孩正在工作（出於尊重，我不會描述她，儘管她虐待了我如此嚴重）。我什至不知道這件事實際上發生了，這對我來說是新聞。但迎接我的是憤怒。公開羞辱和尖叫，我沒有付 400 美元。她多次咒罵我，我保持冷靜。\\n\\n隨後她威脅要報警。超過什麼？顯然她今天過得很糟。\\n\\n我給店主發了訊息——他一開始看起來還不錯。表示他將集中精力進行一些再培訓。\\n\\n然後我又在街上看到那位女同事離開了我要進去的同一家夜總會。她和我的朋友在一起。我過來試著把事情弄清楚，她又開始尖叫——在我看來她表現得很瘋狂。我保持冷靜。不能和這樣說話不肯恭敬的人打交道。\\n\\n我又傳訊息給店主了；讓他知道。\\n\\n他阻止了我。\\n\\n我真的很喜歡這個地方 - 但我想我不再受歡迎了？我很高興我的酒友幫我付了帳單——但我甚至提出再次向工作人員付錢。\\n\\n這給我留下了不好的印象。\\n\\nRude staff, after a misunderstanding and a drinking buddy paying for the 2 beers I forgot to pay for. Returned several times. Then I returned again and then by chance the girl who was working the time the drinking buddy covered the tab was working (who I won\'t describe out of respect even though she mistreated me so badly). I didn\'t even know about this happening actually, it was news to me. But I was greeted with anger. A public shaming and screaming I didn\'t pay 400. She swore at me numerous times I kept my cool.\\n\\nShe then threatened to call the police. Over what? Clearly she had a bad day.\\n\\nI messaged the owner - he seemed ok at first. Said he would focus on some retraining.\\n\\nI then saw the girl colleague in the street again leaving the same night club I was entering. She was with my friend. I came over to try and clear things up, she began screaming again - just in my opinion acting crazy. I remained calm. Can\'t deal with people like this that are unwilling to talk respectfully.\\n\\nI messaged the owner again; to let him know.\\n\\nHe blocked me.\\n\\nI really liked this place - but I guess I\'m not welcome anymore? I\'m glad my drinking buddy covered the tab - but I even offered to pay again to the staff member.\\n\\nThis has left a bad taste in my mouth.\", \"author_name\": \"SM YB\"}]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnsl1lFLeV5FMUxWNKxnBS_x0o9jVud_nDEpkUIaOMkArzBecVCKZfq8oRxyGqtfLlu66B86emmoR97qVb47pc5jVDtjb3rCaRPoI1fPiNUwWE9_NRR6rEG6HXMFQRwlWyICi_pAM-mqlDHQMPJuX21HAYU-anZ7nV6SezdrN87Nqai\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnLUVLPK4JKJHvjQY-PF2t0QgHViR68EYM8ZJynha2RQbH_yVOae5uk4ZLHls8sfImaHAjI45T5WqI_hM9SUT6itNpn_6Dkw_PnfMgHKOgN9KoRkl9hz1rtrzFkpSu32Fn4GfokYMDzn7BTMZlvvreZc_JeKGVpeSVTWHGaPLm7Pn-K\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnMOWByJqx_H-g62Rj7mbgnGlf98qb0OZMjVYk-gA27Dbykg926qLxeXuS0sCNWhZwrhXU5ESrMYCJvwjDdbHpP2NOefKnpRmgbPS9yXZc_Kv0RyPjYR92ACjplIMv5cJj-aNwhA0asOyXSsa3Kwt6mluHBzuCS5eyrduHR8NkJqh-G\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlUACBmzxPm4rPsfpP6G3g63zjG687mIliHJRrV3h-JnokhbJUkqlFPGyIeGSrF0JGWACLDA2VTEddcsVV5dR4n8IGgYY9ETUMUcWul1VgBaduqi8Z7qIUWxy2vjgys9QPEHYuLoCQl5-n3bdmkrDgJyX7z9OyAUSubD9hs6sL1JpkD\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkTtZ77QKivDI4e-3c0tWr3nsf4HpsJFbTajajF8QuFwiEuvCMih2shWnCznhoQFEAoxhRjU7lDy6RqRFRFtnyYXYP4tdf3Thzydr94goKbC8_gz6j5_7x3m2xqbVngA4_OPspxs6sFxYG6GyhkiG_ymByuHehkqyBg4q9hLOjRUzFu\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZknlDNgTjtv5VLJQ4V9xD70ICPoQKmaDh9JGfh8EbNAoBk3hclMG99R70S07l8Ux0B8Wu2r5o4rlWFfNCPAeJrKUL_psCYW7vsjhGPb10rQII07QDOB5ykih-Z6n0EvLusHP4LvUlz3qhF29kK3dQxgGNnQt5Rno6MVP0Ft