不會過溼潤，也不會太乾。冰拿鐵只放了兩顆冰塊，口感很sharp和清新的感覺。豆子感覺比較偏重焙的口感，不會太酸或苦。\\n店家人都很親切，跟這家店給人的感覺一樣！\", \"author_name\": \"Yu-Ching (Frances)\"}, {\"text\": \"寧靜巷弄內向的小店，店內消費普遍偏高，以手沖咖啡為主。店內的氣氛蠻不錯的，很多人在那邊看書跟上網。\", \"author_name\": \"IC\"}, {\"text\": \"位於巷子內\\n店面算大\\n原本以為是塑膠杯的杯子結果就玻璃的\\n質感up\\n手沖咖啡不錯\\n人少的時候滿安靜\\n過兩點半就不少客人開始熱鬧了\", \"author_name\": \"Tom\"}, {\"text\": \"從古亭站/台電大樓站過去的距離是一樣的\\n可以騎U敗過去，那邊很多點可停?\\n在巷弄裡，不過是好找的?\\n門市人員親切??\\n店內的氛圍很舒服?\\n會再回訪??????\", \"author_name\": \"NICK “Nick Liao” LIAO\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZk2xsMayV9sGkbQyJEUaCNPJ4LBZ_RZUvdLO2f2XhZsP5l7HEsChpnTnCEkp25ZuHcFwrNo8lTAnaMp-OmWzOVvyirwkAzF5_LeY45JSs4REJvTv9ENZqsKMUY-G2hAtRUSIFsnZm7pbmc5QTCif-5_bX8-TeXsX0kE-y7PA3w7pqxr\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnYJTdFOzCZQRQIXYrSJnUca-aVIvpllM9Tw3dn5-N5FJD41voc-nOkV6KepxFAi3o6GmN7YuhBed2NUCACHFhJvIdL_nxhogi2naEFO18p9zenHZsBvm-PBSsAW2EhR_UQ5DizYtonO7kxbLVPgbSesUjkL0dEUIvIzX7D5oOw9VEi\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmSCDMgB1gdSAjr72vT2Rx362RF8GiLrzjzqbrYYOX-Yo6u4ZZreHMFEzdITq0ppwLXUs3uDQK7SsHaqe1Qy-p-40ELRLnp3ddsrL-yIFnszw6VciQY4FWLXfTNUu4MioJQqWqvESreYN1zimXdUJeBm_NP_fF9h2YtP1V5dEvV0aLr\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmmb--4u-sMEuK36o7v5ukU2raGdXQQSHE3z6vK5HHXt41ahX2wnAi515Piu2zIAI-Nq9ArnFaHxkKsJsA9oQzts5Dif61SLccipCLnkPN_K-_mJnR-azi08eM_1yjm2JataX9JJh83ImXE-cI64NTHZaLSSG5v7y6ZisiYT6jRI4Gx\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnjePvmLQB0kJBGL-VKgxFIBHCJcorcHDXkFGBbqzekF_E3LpWGb2-9Ef-F3b_4RA2o_t6fOk-nzDaJfOB3sVfdrkQo-4IU4pLxpbo2FnyYADYI-bsJuV0axMdXxcbSx-_bP3Qbm5XVwKgUeWGUOPNR-AlH_mTlh79Eh2Z008S_n6c7\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnjfMO7h-ScF_Nd_XtVG0qdAU24HghBxgxo4Jsj8fryND5Fpu4lOiEcHFn8shijIk4p7K2roeehmXBpRYBSyKjTkTuJ2NaiI6BjCR5E7TKp-woazXplstMf0gCuANmE__jN4nGpIOvUVU25cHXKjf5sAlc8CEJblKnt-JXgF3qPkx3z\"}, {\"widthPx\": 