早期的建築。\\n進去裡面有回到老家的親切感，靜謐的氛圍，也給人悠閑的感覺。不論是三五好友喝下午茶聊天，或是一個人帶著電腦辦公，都是不錯的選擇。\", \"author_name\": \"百看不厭的YenYen\"}, {\"text\": \"小而美，喜歡這種舊式建築又位在小巷中的感覺，氣氛舒適，有貓最棒?\\n很多棕櫚糖食材的餐點，可以來試試～\\n\\n*不過那個蘋果燒肉…建議要重新審視一下…\", \"author_name\": \"尹翔（卡爾先生）\"}, {\"text\": \"小食糖這間咖啡廳隱身在永康商圈巷內的老宅變身餐廳的小確幸，到處有文青的氣息，老闆用棕櫚糖做蛋糕、食材，不昇血糖，蠻健康的！\\n蛋糕現做，口感也不錯，現場空間氛圍很舒服！細細品味咖啡處理手上的事情！很不錯?！\\n還有看到店貓，很可愛！非常適合來這邊喝一個悠閑的下午茶！\", \"author_name\": \"品晟 Steven沈一傑\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZm3pIk7qRS9eaZruzLRalSp8I4107-8oU_R4nUmKkF_SOmPoAZBqZZdqfUI7Pjr78cneQJ-IsteUlt_jg_CNIhqVEQ7mWJo-ltPus_IBhA95qHwP-b1MnfaSaWBeLB3XQ_LgQ2anixV_N0YyjiouTQYWzASmwt2VvgnaBTC0mnGaqy8\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZna7IxVnEzyLqGdEsmk-GmeqvBn4QKHeufiH0mluseIIlpvCPl_fxUEMH4wPnaIm5feuDbUHRgkTCTC9FiKPhJq2K2fZ83aausEbTOJkzwUNbZS29QbJJhAIs8X2sX6iKKidNXms1wFZ87fGV9a9QurKOflUIQJSSNmKSJuj4mXjhFp\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnYnBF2jz_O9hhg4wtM7psyJItGSQoc5vjXvN_Lor4Cpztp-tzwQBDf10Urto9Uymd7wEkep7D3j23mp7_Dsigh8l5NYEA_l5OJusS0g3TEk9HjPCxdLNeCQZRRIJEp3RCMmrT_oMvfJryO7y2sTv9uzpetkh5mQYbMf3kLfu5i-a0d\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmN_wiGffqEocPH2bY3MuOyy_mMHa4bIks0XWHQb8s4IN_sfFk0pKaOlzfYQpDghxAgDWnzlPDbRmmal01TU-Z_19QERtOTCnsYjUvsfSVlGuYSoUfnCQzDYZsaoJ1SQTNOeq0LjT7c6e5y-lkdPk7SyzmVmMEFQiw49t_FkuxHMWhV\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmZQILP4Fs30EgYNQLPz_Qa4HE-SFdew_fWrU8t1T7YyegYqjF_9PuWtygWSDYbgZddOulKxr7zA75l4LvmsBlPKfLQTovJscFpy_gTIZwsmv7mxodDoUK43wBNB4LALyPzHE7Dp6NihkAFLb2RZdTwAfohbiZakyKvwJnvPdjW93CP\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZk_DEhtifEZc9_FWDUhT7jHHcb1T1EJ63C_K-lva5SXjfsITkGdZdHW8r09Tpc_ngmB4I22bEigo3vIhnKryh7W1oN-HCi5a8e4UvxwzIHZGO_KCQxywFgVEFl1gpVHHlwtKBczJ89BWtRqPG45pzyHI2yq_IhBKVLi23V390k_975D\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkgf_ihbtI