TZU\"}, {\"text\": \"位台北忠孝新生捷運站?五號出口的咖啡館?，真的慕名而來，像是城市中的小綠洲，非常chill沒有壓力，露天咖啡廳的意境，天氣好的時候很舒服。店員很熱情親切，咖啡甜點都很滿意，手沖咖啡☕️風味多層次。時常到忠孝新生站?搭捷運時，都會隨手外帶一杯。\", \"author_name\": \"林立綸\"}, {\"text\": \"閒空時的放鬆好去處❤️\\n咖啡香濃，店員熱情健談。\\n每一杯咖啡都很用心，從挑豆，磨豆，沖豆，每一個細節都是做到最最最好。\\n用心泡出來的豆子就是非常棒，非常好喝\\n咖啡香醇再加一點音樂再加一點休閒的聊天，真的是無比的放鬆\", \"author_name\": \"CH小劇場 chen\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmkgNWUXyx1ekfqx8rW-I4CQiDB-rwgffJnQLr4JjFLRpcgk0DY-e-rGHZ8P9GLV62kzxGLWqP4YzWVPzbgO-6ZgGJgsO8jIep07Q73Mvv3G8Z5FxUZs9t2zdPNueSGEBYGMqPdsdHKsan6kHxoVEl7uJbztRvqr1EkctYDL3brdKNY\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmDDLKrZswIVwqOo39zPR55s1IML-GqFbPTa1EgJQLj_Kb9sSZsPpHISE4UO9qV50Zl12drIstb5cc5lig_ZyFWjY--1FZ37ww31CbbwfWoIomkHqdY6mIMcoEZlWjksGOwEFgb4abaYd8wsdNj4UU_X9qDsQgE-79ntRw1tcHNw6n0\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkXpKTy75m2kEApbcDXw3_wgdtBpZdkJNOxPwjAYiy_45wIOOT5wgiWGA9SxXqTXxeYBYuZHlibg6qcaBfo4NVY4WVDkNQykqPonUEOt9pAYwVwI_dNA2Faf3oqfGU1ksPiKJ_aMHvWWdS9FA4XR7663XbDXd5JhjKHjBRa8IWP6SSN\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkj2k2SMR2_vPc_CQBAB1HJxnZtFbaQ6d7xhvTNmoOOrZ7eA6k2HgmAmphBFGOkhW_9pYzYeeE7wbUg1BemMgO9fZUXvqUzxiqF3Mi71NDoXYmeDK2dpIw8EeapPC4qnshE1Br6kyAdVMKDzAArz777OrheXEaIuBPKWyBAxMqQv9T1\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnSrtTtJLfGOC6aXNBn3Wp2WeShjiTfBnx93jatTdsC5-zonIy3yZZHT-De0QWbkoWoEwDsfI87ZJjrtnTOwhCjeyyB6WzPq9EobsFrV-whVf-8OPL7TCpAZy8_-v2ZUulz81QiU7_IV-iiTmBiLJpTBgkVE0gV_d8KUmKhjqEfgvI\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkZR5yPCSpXU00rh74ZvPcphq_lpKAxNV-Y2KNGi6_17WYjUotmryPDcoxoJx9S455zIiw8elLdKLABEu9cyUYgRKtq4izAAPZET8rdEYEV6TsJwtOoPsFBImJRj4pdrQkGjCkTPzqAYZC0XvnP4suyFnqukBIG3oyiivgxw2NV0SAb\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZk3gk0SxU1W6NMPXjL68xTUTTSnbp2Uwqd6nWz0smy8P0j11F4KboyR_1YTV7NGFL3XR0dA61chOW1Apv4wFyN8pVXte6Vmic6