"text\": \"西門町的咖啡店\\n店內空間偏小、座位也不太多\\n很容易客滿，但是不會覺得太擠，整個空間是讓人家覺得很舒服的配置\\n\\n生意非常得好，老闆本來想要去外面彈個手風琴，結果到了戶外彈個1分鐘之後，人就開始絡繹不絕的湧進，後來老闆就再也沒有時間碰他的他的手風琴了。\\n\\n是一家同志友好的咖啡廳，\\n餐廳裡面非常多老闆的小巧思，連衛生紙都是用彩虹圖案的舒潔。每一道飲品上來的時候，旁邊都會有一個動物的裝飾品，超級可愛的，害我好想把所有飲品一次點光，看老闆會有多少個動物裝飾品\", \"author_name\": \"C Rabbit\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkNz3CpRgKHDhbyRu_EqMw8CRuVueBZhPbm7c361RvIviT-X9IaiOvwa9ia2eXgzQ1ZdpSB9oKLW0GoJYgdyakaW59EfPchWEA7KnWXF5aMumfsl5c8N5yDI5ERdN0uAaYTy810gWR-81jnQHR5f0QCKMqED8w5dRG0TZbkeciuYpI\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZndm47o2OjVHfXpTbw451Q25QTF-50OsMEnF3uo_0HTNxcTuKO154QJaxX1XjaUGDyjpDh32PF6_LGBfK_HrWH1Dv3kGkpCJzYc5wgN4bNz0mUaaAmL5Pp5TSR0t-fFeliiwU-azojO9ydOz0aufq5hI_LsuUauyX4XIBD1N_9FsnI\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnSVrHKPedn0O8Mx79Id7WB5rNwrQ6DUjvvkLsgkPeUTdd-J_huIYOGl9euSM5s5YmuMW7I-F0i-JxzEa8Tbx3J6flCJgqCnRoK19SKdPRBOorDjhLLzfoXrnrY-vIroCeJPiwTipw0KvylyGjhye0A5E7ALPncqWpPSALuoP-1Eekg\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkLkgoB0seCqz8yE71MGYUzLsgsPgjMk6adSfYUbbxBihvj14gPWMBjavR21ADqYd55jbpXRu_mYsgzNHwUE6w_Wcwxv8NmwiPr4pt5Eb_MNgLX1x630hptdlpYZXHXICia8mUNqVb3CpYmnXFGKyDStFE3VyA_26GjtIEDzuBNDVU\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZl0Oef3YmUybC5ONhiuP8KllK8b3lHTH6Lnfp1koYaE6wQ_Aqv5idZiz90WB3MwewS6bNYqTOTD8IQN8g-M4r__xFmc8iy6-N2FfMP89X5UE_Ynr5Jq_wAuJjViLtbyoVYZcvou5tLWMuOoUMRiBJUyPKBYE7Z_YBRFLRUghuoqQ3Ov\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZk288wJl2qxF0koVn0LSgd920q0rvNUHuXf1hXNZw0lXXU_o_g9ThSGp6Ic2rkj-MCUt0nEtLYvdO7seECqi2Kwwul4swtIF9VkuyB8IwdWCm6LVYQzDFF0TPe67oHuNgcJz6FLMYMCdTaoB1pFOLBVuBL3t4LqHhpuc07ZaGYkqh-7\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnugTP6m7oCcuWKXqDvl0ggZEQzOU_QOmGOTieNWS4ssM2cqsQUy1kdqFTCUeORYHlqZ2A1MM-ysaPN3H9zs6Herm7ikrlNCQD5QPK2loTofJ5vIUJRThMQnBr3vFkHKRBOaL-3mxSdKuC7lnu9Z0NBk