uthor_name\": \"Cami Liu\"}, {\"text\": \"身為甜點寶可夢大師應該不需多說了吧\\n台北妹妹都會知道的公園咖啡\\n招牌酥皮蘋果派加冰淇淋堪稱神之手等級\\n脆口的蘋果派體跟入口即化的冰淇淋無須多言 肉桂粉與內餡蘋果脆片提升風味\\n層次跟口感很豐富 配上奶油美式 我會哭\\n\\n懂得人就懂 看到發條橘子的海報會多麼興奮\\n店內許多陳設極具品味\\n還有看到不少畫展及當代藝術展覽資訊\\n店內藏書也令人感受到懷舊氣息\\n\\n難以忘懷的店！\", \"author_name\": \"yixin Li\"}, {\"text\": \"二訪～不限時超棒（但因為人很多較吵雜）\\n?派很酥+冰淇淋好吃\\n私心很推蘑菇鮭魚鹹派！！超級美味>  ̫\", \"author_name\": \"mu\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnmi007LETDyYswg-vt_irJydXuo9EemA4Z_m0_nJdHZPkyo7CD4wam0rAjorXUhfjJ8IBiJKUG1GvvMcUUFyca2UReEOUZVGaYjt2PoB2KYg_N-ULQ53Iq6L1gNVcByZRc74sXHEJLBkGMR92OoEmq2SPWb0RkrLVMCXM3hFq5WrQn\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlN5UKiWLNKbO3wTcfRJbhSBfQQIyqTL6qnMcDLBYSCnjMhXpS4mBiuNYo8MDhGj3FuuI1hUCEZITpROPIVV_T_9BOcHLCwy6uz91aujIE5cOOEsSktfjmyDEWG1Kv56C-BwCDbhWXYQ95ZmFQjfHUnpU-uAXM1l_eU9a82Du6rc5si\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZm0sAxTyGieW4r3MLgFB-E8tq_6bGInHo5po_LC-IMM-llk59Dbo-_YZ8-cLSNHEJ3mF5GsCr3yMIrxR9M0qBSYD0Wabg324iw2SOdUmetU6gfEDdeDoewg9ogXZSuRSNgAwsaVOZ9njwXinipbxZRBqKwDV4mNPSQDbH8W7D0loc-G\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlrBfk9aH92EKxAbIb64iMEEkZnptwi6kg880HYG3GxGtxnnYqaRJhZmL_HzOeGcHp5TGc6vVmbPuOrL5zsuthBcFwFQwvOTfFd2guHGzOJTC_NX5Yximso1eSynHZHIohWWS9RphWRlqWwiVMn6O2OOTXUeWcDt1dzzZicuT2fyZmw\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZm6LnwWzp-Vaz2MtutPpbG-Os04fZ9HAw7cU7CRDzCdav3u2h-50DFKg5tRaigu99cy-o4Nuv8T2Ep4AxKA8YBelVV4N3u9RkH-Ab0mJ97mHwG3bx4kTPBYBrchCW2NcdoZbF0TuYqUwQEVSK0KrUe3TzoTu2txbiX1IcjLnW7s60rE\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnRiOyoSpzeU71Gc6J4vXgzGJNFiZgMxQR4cJC-7E9dwVWnOsZluLMObWgXFlCGAAzo8N_-w2BFb9hgrTgVoUAia5O-rk8Gaz83ZeQRFKt32N3qZEQHama5dAUtmuyGiR4E-zMYNBTZpGbuIi1vNkkQq6k_Bdq82nBCffmEtq9-T9Mb\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlVJJBzOdztYhaswziblIw5daHHageu8wjaE_csyknQhwH_lmj-qtIud6