虛有其表，結果試了才知道冰品都是下足功夫的！\\n\\n首先擂茶冰非常濃郁但卻絲毫不甜膩，搭配花生和米香真的感覺自己在客家三合院，上面不惜成本放上金箔，網美效果十足。小缺點可能有些擂茶粉會讓人無法邊吃邊講話。\\n\\n番茄羅勒冰這個真的牛逼，原本是放在瑪格麗特披薩上的配料放在冰上意外的搭，尤其是馬茲瑞拉起司鹹甜的口感令人欲罷不能，而且作法繁瑣，需要先把番茄汁解凍再打成汁才能有這一小碗冰。\\n\\n食物以外的細節也都很用心，雖然個人不是很愛但是整體很整潔乾淨，連廁所都很用心。相信不只是網美連男生都會覺得是個舒適的環境！\\n\\n不過價格偏高，可能偶爾回訪。題外話那天地震真的很大欸～\", \"author_name\": \"Peng James\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmIZfT6A7Cvnfl-rG5lcl5sZ35UBZj3Ganpw240dITwplMjVkVQLVxtNMOfjNZnJvT4jVJNQwB_5C-tBjunxuBApuE_6N6Q5s7MgZIDCKjlwpJqcN7ywRZkjGzb0TGFepmtNl3s_ACxzFP5Z-BoQxcLiRo8-r8fydX92LGfk9gHddtJ\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmINzIgef8shW9aTEvr8alZktRf2PBIgp0lX67ljDH_YYFHBsmLQS-K1OsLLQaeXdi5kFIvnL0-6Jl2WsahK9Ub8_YGqHE3y_fV9KrAjUvOA9DeDuBRGGKDQ2__gdUIgCUrm6LZeqRCKLtw82-IYPVKIc9UHnSMgHToPo6uLEm7IyRe\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZn-gXdIV_geXLBL8d5bOo_xOuCepKoMRMwff9FZhohEksvjNWy9KpwGXpW_jRZr-GkLP-nI6RM5znc-eOQVfN-Wgz5WPJNvyNsO3QzAzhaCJnQ8oPkZ-h7yXl7eUvb4ufG53otQoveO9jEHfcu-u1uVTo-UhM8bQZGk7EuAF01Ey10W\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlaYBn9T-5mWbJc0OIjfA-zjM7_Jo7VcmFVfBpWxem02PCFcSczFaLN2MblmOXzSy_ESAkqHvHftu8yyaJO0u96lHpjwO9XqnQ4ho2p1Fc1gMAizH02wVTG2vAdrXnHDS6MoHNr4jlxbJPfC5XRx6YtXRGwBvINKNXxjvUfA8zejImo\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZn_hfACVB21MsPv6Lv3bT33DyBC6EIf5_PyWxBnplBSjA4M2_yrqrH7B7enNpnAqEwnnAbhfNGGstHv3XZ-oJlvXbwRJJrD08Y-jNBLMr1RtsyWpd110BsmFHjPZwjBMNOHQv26SmQoMMXXUKtljQt54VmR2AiCMIV6rJ9_G8l5sFtQ\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmzdeiqIcIeLrbIvOKGbRbS_jnGrKSAEStn3LaNhxIIckVIFAM8oqbEiyWIV7hsh5GLXC3I7Ip_qYSsFYhbfwEiMMVr_AIuEiUXAAUH4H1AxDe818JA_VkqyYx9g6_FE6MI1w8ZhbtLv0QvuNfeWDb7kc4MmQVc_qXNDQkA9QVSq25G\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmVfTGWAHECbOiitH9IUzIO3I4wb75NE3ZCs0jkk4DU4MZvPmnY3zqa5VxMeox5D2Nq9tKKkXofrHWFoezkQhwOabUQjjC83d0dW0h