和老闆說要甜筒裝，不然會變成杯裝，視覺效果差很多呢\", \"author_name\": \"李幸珍\"}, {\"text\": \"老闆娘、非常親切，也很好聊！！！\\n奶油胡桃非常好吃，味濃、還有隱約的鹹味；\\n開心果不甜，非常適合怕甜的人。重點、都可以吃的到堅果粒。日後一定固定來訪。\", \"author_name\": \"benmih Chu\"}, {\"text\": \"沙拉份量很大，冰淇淋口味很多很特別，因為都是自製所以口味很多，口味比較重，吃到老闆的私房料理，希望能快上市\", \"author_name\": \"張馬克\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmweTkncfu_gRZHCNVDFcPRJBq-r8-AJF1_wTf3kz7NLA2X4s4hb4Jbyyjm17cXcwAExDlXxrUHLGZqN3jLKSb95Q0VxgZFLDEe21_iZVxb_XUUYFVr6UUkLfGLhJQrGTg8O3W7HqE-EvCEIMYo_e9L30QJQres2LGJ8qrdaaQIdQXm\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnoYOx9ytHQZTnEb8PYMMOWvRRDsrdHPQWUn4DzHrJMhNksYVQcT5fLOq3GU5oK70kslpmWiojMhon4Gwz7oJVjX9f3XwkGJkeE1kzC-UghIThcsmHZw7ziZIQp8cfBUTvMnhp7sWdpQTx4qBID5gjWdmvZB_P5aIK0Qz0YryJdErxl\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZn4cTiCc-VbGdFbk_Pw9EehyHBGzMkhd83vyLph7Ia-oLN8kT2fjlEduhaSJHtGqrZT4W20U53_slLwXXqiu92tT0SImTxTDbuZ1sLH0jHdnaPHfUxg82qYBuKVePyKB7pro71oGzk8rwan9M8bOJ1vQG6kxUWEzvhJYnAJ3FoScXoV\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZlptoqYmDpztr3PD8WhHVMaoF4LwOxvGs1GrqTBOO3LZpKST5ylqn5JbC5Mtl1DGX5_EgFdQOg-gL50G21CWHVSl112QEX76hxZRA5Z6Uv_jdAkhfdf671vhKSyLHK7mYX3aNa90yyOeAKsOSeZHRyIpXetUn_-bjlcq8eJSLZ9bEIm\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkbyU76EMUWK5ZOQphKEDTjlo5yQxMOaefJ5RR66XMEAN28k7w_lwRkvbCD_LG97N0HW5_g2iWI5OU4YpmbcyNv6SyUZXAlAc_ycNPw6xSaBvDSbOk5Dm3hBzETt6Iqc7I0w1VROVYbWI2NxClO9BRI9oTvklrqn6JlP5fcktusOxnU\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZloqQ_WeWgLkUJSfoBSlJp5du1Rb69Ho_pZWg2iwIxEgb7qHkehasx21NlyUdE1EUj6yOLKaeBPhbInPY6BZiUN9GPD5UDPnMzuL-kyWqwprKx_Hi0ChAnebQq846iLoTSFz7YFdLEVXeHHrFE7nfcyGDtrEPLbp8vZ1xbrnmHCZwo_\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnH02nI1qEcry2Gr_jc0rvR49ZLeJG5dUvR1HkVSirMKDZ_LbE6-ExrSd4oapP-0o4Fm_AoVMNCd6WLnZuQRtkkXkvNoHmFd2-3AtTp-0FVCWSVBKrt1407rho867_n6VzN__7MUn8i4Mr7SQzcA5iKfg