or_name\": \"ASKA LIN\"}, {\"text\": \"檸檬柚子和百香優格清爽好吃！\", \"author_name\": \"Catherine Chen\"}, {\"text\": \"請問冰淇淋蛋糕有外送嗎 謝謝\\n老闆可以幫我傳一下口味有多少 謝謝（剛有打電話詢問）\", \"author_name\": \"盧伶雅\"}, {\"text\": \"小朋友生日,訂了這個蛋糕，老闆很用心，包裝很漂亮，連蠟燭，紙盤都很可愛，還有附保冰袋和冰寶。重點是冰淇淋真的好好吃。基底是香草和百香果。上面的冰淇淋球是根據我的需求，全部都是水果的。黑色的那一顆特別好吃，一開始大家都覺得很熟悉吃不出來是什麼味道，後來發現是柳丁，而且是台灣柳丁的味道。好好吃。\", \"author_name\": \"Sophy Yeh\"}]','[]','[{\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmdDxlJGO_UnydEzErW4Zd6944UB1L3y6SIbJxKr__GmbCtYmVvXCnug1DVQPjlfVG83udhrRbc03NBneNmJ1r5_LZ9gDLayXduQ6s7dKqSRmZQyJY7ErdRFd9ZXAfcyu6nnbWX2BEf3dUmAoYG0AG5AlgAH-YiAPEwejKtWgloCvQV\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZknvju7sEGTM6JJ4HMU_4dCvfu6NLssOaY2jiOCNA2i5xF5qVctS7qgav3Vrax6Ovs0TUIkcQzRgg0ilJ2i95-Hea7_dmr5rhhMzzVdVV5tOKYlwjVssDHPVMlG3AdZVspxFR0to78LFVgYgRQrvTBGr0OYzTXAjSny5HLs1sbmrKrL\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnSiuh410nauorwgHt1JU9dPWf2TN-ZsatIZjTOOf42QQG5All_4tuuRbqTilyJe3lE_bhMSqWF1N28BkSt0ZM9UcIiHaXWuLeEg6ngatw7iK6_PtO9WtAi3rHS3x0789y4CToVS3lj4RSSdv_-4jZlu4tGtswt9zbhiQ_IxVb-id9b\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZm01PxzF3Qor-R3uy-NkVosi7r-Sc31x1RxLfR76YQTP1uUa5HpjRLxy3CZvlHV-AewLlZ4-tqPSFFfIa54YP8xUxaCQMtd7e9XSBERC5vEHA7SNPu220OAVzp3NCPtFnha7j6GNgx-nyfr581fdvz_381o5s6Vc8smk70RpDXoIaDb\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZnsJIFp_TWUIKVSq0-VEP9UPxVRJVJImOqgjVDgwND4qkzL4JJ-0rtQoOawtzPWfHR7QNp_ht_RqvkVrHzeJyZM3i-uPwVZ3ojZPgqabYencvaPGMwxGpOciSajtHs9psoH38oA3xeizlLCaLG0PCViXjbDidkyAHRtXhQMoOZNdTNc\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZmkmA3c3xjNLQNCywvbzKoMMyCXGEnWruXZa2B9j206A0d5brydQXG4zI0JqyKM0bpDa2I_jrOm2bDK83zeUSp7zxxj1lOWYQBJduYeCFZDY4bcHUGGk6ercnWz7D0c4bSdpWkarPkplLJTGjSdG32RUxEVmPRbPQpcDK40EOYOXq9f\"}, {\"widthPx\": 4000, \"heightPx\": 6000, \"photo_reference\": \"AUGGfZkYEVsCFafWsZ1QNiwDpE4xR9JToOJACUN6UxQ_95T15Dek1H0j5hXgFzo